      <h1>XML Schema 1.1</h1>
      <p>Saxon-EE from release 9.3 includes support for most of the new features introduced in the XML Schema 1.1 working drafts. The main changes
are listed in the following pages. Note that these features are subject to change as the specifications mature.</p>
      <p>To enable use of XML Schema 1.1 features, set the command line flag <code>-xsdversion:1.1</code> or the equivalent
in the API.</p>
